WEBVTT

00:18.240 --> 00:19.380
You may leave.

00:26.400 --> 00:29.500
Still yearning for it, Your Highness?

00:32.680 --> 00:34.690
The most tempting things

00:36.240 --> 00:38.370
are often those that harm us.

00:39.740 --> 00:42.420
I was thinking we could

00:42.600 --> 00:43.920
have a smoke together.

00:45.440 --> 00:46.650
I came in such a hurry,

00:47.200 --> 00:48.580
I forgot to bring mine.

00:49.160 --> 00:50.300
Use mine.

00:50.590 --> 00:51.730
I dare not.

00:52.200 --> 00:54.460
During your absence,

00:55.440 --> 00:56.860
I've already quit this habit.

01:02.460 --> 01:05.600
You always say you dare not.

01:06.060 --> 01:08.440
Yet the only person who dares to defy me

01:10.460 --> 01:11.680
is you.

01:14.140 --> 01:16.280
Congratulations on returning safely

01:18.020 --> 01:19.560
from Lizhen.

01:20.380 --> 01:21.520
If there's nothing else,

01:21.820 --> 01:22.960
I shall take my leave.

01:23.060 --> 01:24.600
I haven't allowed you to leave.

01:24.860 --> 01:26.739
I want to hear your music,

01:26.740 --> 01:28.600
just like in the old days.

01:29.420 --> 01:31.680
Just like my smoking habit,

01:32.380 --> 01:33.520
my guqin

01:34.740 --> 01:36.600
has long been gathering dust.

01:42.860 --> 01:44.520
That's the Duke of Jining's
signal flare.

01:45.360 --> 01:46.520
Miss!

01:47.520 --> 01:48.840
Ming is missing!

01:48.980 --> 01:50.939
Madam has sent people
to search everywhere.

01:50.940 --> 01:53.090
It's been two hours,
and they still haven't found her.

01:53.100 --> 01:55.059
(She left when she wasn't selected.)

01:55.060 --> 01:56.400
(She was never seen again.)

01:57.820 --> 01:59.360
(Could they be together?)

01:59.780 --> 02:00.979
The guards are nearby.

02:00.980 --> 02:01.910
I'll go gather the men.

02:01.920 --> 02:03.000
My lord.

02:05.820 --> 02:07.760
The Duke cares most
about his reputation.

02:07.780 --> 02:09.110
This matter cannot be made public.

02:09.660 --> 02:11.920
Why don't I go with you?

03:32.660 --> 03:36.779
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

03:36.780 --> 03:40.040
=Episode 15=

03:46.300 --> 03:47.440
I'll go check first.

03:47.460 --> 03:48.760
Please come later.

03:50.260 --> 03:51.680
How could you be so careless?

03:53.220 --> 03:54.720
I didn't see it.

03:55.420 --> 03:56.560
Never mind.

04:01.740 --> 04:02.880
Fourth Young Lady.

04:04.460 --> 04:05.600
Sister!

04:08.900 --> 04:10.400
No, it's not what you think.

04:11.140 --> 04:13.219
You see, I wasn't selected.

04:13.220 --> 04:14.480
I was feeling upset.

04:14.820 --> 04:17.120
Then I saw a little rabbit.

04:17.840 --> 04:20.099
Fourth Young Lady,
please don't blame Fifth Young Lady.

04:20.100 --> 04:22.499
We saw a rabbit

04:22.500 --> 04:23.529
and wanted to set it free.

04:23.530 --> 04:24.419
Yes.

04:24.420 --> 04:26.040
We led the horse here on foot.

04:26.180 --> 04:27.720
Nothing inappropriate happened.

04:31.100 --> 04:32.240
What happened to your foot?

04:32.500 --> 04:34.179
I twisted it by accident just now.

04:34.180 --> 04:35.320
It's nothing.

04:36.460 --> 04:37.880
This place is so remote.

04:38.580 --> 04:40.080
You can't ride horses anymore.

04:40.260 --> 04:41.399
You'll have to ride with me.

04:41.400 --> 04:42.259
- I'm fine.
- I'm fine.

04:42.260 --> 04:43.900
- Take her back first.
- Take him back first.

04:50.900 --> 04:53.400
You are engaged to him.

04:53.580 --> 04:56.320
It's only reasonable for you two
to ride back together.

04:56.380 --> 04:57.520
When you arrive,

04:57.580 --> 04:59.339
just send someone to pick me up.

04:59.340 --> 05:00.720
That doesn't seem very reasonable.

05:00.940 --> 05:03.179
Even though they're engaged,
they're not married yet.

05:03.180 --> 05:04.520
It's still inappropriate.

05:05.380 --> 05:07.000
The Duke and I share a bond.

05:07.060 --> 05:08.530
Naturally, I should take him back.

05:10.140 --> 05:11.280
A bond?

05:13.820 --> 05:14.960
It's just a dislocation.

05:19.940 --> 05:21.459
I admire your poise,

05:21.460 --> 05:23.040
though you're a bit frail.

05:26.140 --> 05:27.760
When you join the Imperial Guard,

05:27.780 --> 05:28.920
I'll personally mentor you.

05:30.500 --> 05:31.640
Thank you, Lord Song.

05:34.180 --> 05:35.320
The Imperial Guard?

05:45.740 --> 05:46.880
Fourth Young Lady.

05:47.500 --> 05:48.640
Are you alright?

05:55.030 --> 05:55.979
Sorry.

05:55.980 --> 05:57.120
I'm so sorry.

05:57.300 --> 05:58.139
Are you alright?

05:58.140 --> 05:58.979
Mr. Dong,

05:58.980 --> 06:00.179
the hunt is over now.

06:00.180 --> 06:02.060
Why are you still shooting arrows
everywhere?

06:02.460 --> 06:04.520
Everyone, I sincerely apologize.

06:04.540 --> 06:06.520
Lord Song was wearing brown clothing,

06:06.860 --> 06:08.520
and I mistook him for a brown bear.

06:08.660 --> 06:09.659
I was startled

06:09.660 --> 06:10.800
and shot an arrow.

06:11.340 --> 06:12.560
I'm truly sorry.

06:14.180 --> 06:15.320
Fourth Young Lady,

06:15.340 --> 06:16.480
are you okay?

06:16.540 --> 06:17.419
Zhao,

06:17.420 --> 06:18.560
are you alright?

06:22.980 --> 06:24.120
I'm fine.

06:24.140 --> 06:25.379
Where on earth did they go?

06:25.380 --> 06:26.979
- Father.
- Ming!

06:26.980 --> 06:28.099
- Mother.
- Ming!

06:28.100 --> 06:29.259
Where have you been?

06:29.260 --> 06:30.339
Are you alright?

06:30.340 --> 06:31.810
I went to the forest to clear my head.

06:31.820 --> 06:32.619
I got lost.

06:32.620 --> 06:34.440
Luckily, my sister found me.

06:36.660 --> 06:38.539
Nanny Zhou, quickly escort Ming back.

06:38.540 --> 06:40.219
- I'll take her back myself.
- Alright.

06:40.220 --> 06:41.360
Come on, Ming.

06:41.780 --> 06:43.500
- Are you alright?
- I'm fine.

06:44.020 --> 06:45.360
You silly child.

06:46.740 --> 06:47.880
Stop right there.

06:49.340 --> 06:51.280
Competing to win the Emperor's favor.

06:51.500 --> 06:52.499
How much longer

06:52.500 --> 06:54.200
will you disgrace the Dou family?

06:54.660 --> 06:56.680
You still dream of serving the court?

06:56.740 --> 06:58.200
Are you even capable of that?

06:58.540 --> 06:59.720
Don't think I don't know.

06:59.940 --> 07:01.080
You're just trying

07:01.180 --> 07:03.720
to delay your marriage
to the Duke of Jining.

07:04.300 --> 07:05.440
And another thing,

07:05.780 --> 07:08.320
a woman participating in gambling...

07:09.060 --> 07:11.420
Do you want to drag
the entire Dou family down with you?

07:12.260 --> 07:14.880
Don't think you can get away with this
by staying silent.

07:18.340 --> 07:19.560
Walking out on me now?

07:19.860 --> 07:21.480
She's like a different person.

07:22.140 --> 07:23.280
Stop right there!

07:25.340 --> 07:27.720
Why didn't she talk back today?

07:28.020 --> 07:29.560
Fine, I won't press further.

07:50.660 --> 07:52.440
(Once again, life hangs by a thread.)

07:53.540 --> 07:55.520
(Is fate truly inevitable?)

07:56.220 --> 07:58.280
(Can we never escape this arrow?)

08:08.300 --> 08:09.760
You once told me,

08:10.820 --> 08:12.280
if I gather enough strength,

08:13.020 --> 08:14.560
I can topple mountains

08:14.580 --> 08:15.720
and reverse rivers.

08:16.100 --> 08:18.000
I've already changed so much.

08:18.220 --> 08:19.680
Why does it still turn out this way?

08:22.160 --> 08:24.200
All things have their fate.

08:24.400 --> 08:26.700
Cause and effect are cyclical.

08:27.380 --> 08:29.930
Look at that large rock in the water.

08:30.400 --> 08:32.280
Though it weighs a hundred pounds,

08:32.620 --> 08:35.880
it can only split
a single stream of water.

08:36.340 --> 08:40.360
In the end, everything still gathers
behind the large rock.

08:41.620 --> 08:43.019
One person's strength

08:43.020 --> 08:45.240
is insignificant

08:45.580 --> 08:48.400
in the grand river of history.

08:49.900 --> 08:51.440
All things are predestined.

08:53.980 --> 08:55.920
So nothing can really change.

09:21.260 --> 09:22.379
What's wrong?

09:22.380 --> 09:23.680
What happened?

09:24.500 --> 09:25.510
Nothing.

09:25.520 --> 09:26.460
If I hadn't stopped you,

09:26.470 --> 09:27.860
you would've fallen into the river.

09:28.880 --> 09:29.920
What's wrong?

09:31.500 --> 09:34.680
Maybe it's because
I haven't eaten anything.

09:35.580 --> 09:36.800
I feel a bit weak.

09:43.540 --> 09:44.680
You know,

09:45.220 --> 09:46.520
when I first joined the army,

09:46.620 --> 09:48.120
I worked as a cook.

09:49.060 --> 09:50.960
This is a reunion dish from Futing.

09:51.180 --> 09:52.779
Vegetables, meat, eggs...

09:52.780 --> 09:53.920
Anything goes in.

09:55.780 --> 09:57.920
It's called Fortune Soup.

09:59.060 --> 10:00.200
It smells amazing.

10:00.340 --> 10:02.000
My mother used to make it for me.

10:02.020 --> 10:04.059
Every time, she'd add something new.

10:04.060 --> 10:05.360
Mushrooms, seafood,

10:05.380 --> 10:06.520
anything, really.

10:06.700 --> 10:07.840
She said,

10:07.860 --> 10:09.200
life is like that.

10:09.260 --> 10:11.139
It's like an old dish
you're used to eating.

10:11.140 --> 10:12.190
Add a few new ingredients,

10:12.200 --> 10:14.080
and the flavor becomes
completely different.

10:14.380 --> 10:15.520
That's true.

10:16.260 --> 10:17.800
Everything is changing.

10:18.580 --> 10:21.160
Just like how Father
will have a new lover,

10:22.060 --> 10:23.600
new children,

10:23.900 --> 10:25.040
and a new family.

10:26.260 --> 10:28.000
Every family experiences conflict

10:28.020 --> 10:29.499
due to legitimacy, seniority,

10:29.500 --> 10:30.680
status and rank.

10:31.100 --> 10:32.440
Everyone is vying for themselves

10:32.700 --> 10:34.200
and their children.

10:34.210 --> 10:36.120
When the Lizhen troops arrived
at Zhenbei Pass,

10:36.130 --> 10:37.960
a son born out of wedlock
started a rebellion.

10:38.260 --> 10:40.160
When strife happens
within the imperial family,

10:40.380 --> 10:43.080
it becomes a state affair.

10:44.260 --> 10:45.800
Now that you have the Emperor's favor

10:45.980 --> 10:47.280
and military power,

10:47.430 --> 10:49.979
the Crown Prince and Lord Qing
will surely try to win you over.

10:49.980 --> 10:51.280
What do you plan to do?

10:52.340 --> 10:53.480
I plan to

10:54.260 --> 10:55.400
copy you.

10:55.800 --> 10:56.960
Copy me?

10:58.180 --> 10:59.379
The current Song Mo

10:59.380 --> 11:01.000
has long let go of hatred.

11:01.020 --> 11:02.680
He focuses only on fame and fortune.

11:03.420 --> 11:05.040
I'll observe their moves first

11:05.180 --> 11:08.220
before deciding what to do.

11:32.460 --> 11:33.600
Someone's coming.

11:34.020 --> 11:35.160
Hide.

11:57.440 --> 11:58.880
I haven't had the Fortune Soup yet.

12:07.280 --> 12:08.520
You have something on your mind.

12:09.620 --> 12:11.200
You've been off all day.

12:11.940 --> 12:13.280
What exactly happened?

12:21.620 --> 12:22.760
The arrow.

12:23.630 --> 12:25.120
It has something to do with the arrow.

12:25.820 --> 12:27.760
How could a single arrow
cause this much alarm?

12:35.180 --> 12:37.400
You think you can read my mind,
don't you?

12:38.180 --> 12:39.680
Be it today's incident

12:39.700 --> 12:41.280
or Wei Tingyu's situation,

12:42.140 --> 12:44.320
does reading my thoughts
make you fulfilled?

12:45.920 --> 12:47.280
Reading faces and noticing details

12:47.500 --> 12:49.880
was a skill I used
to interrogate criminals.

12:49.980 --> 12:51.379
Most of them were tortured.

12:51.380 --> 12:52.379
Their limbs broken.

12:52.380 --> 12:53.949
Some even bit off their own tongues.

12:53.950 --> 12:55.739
♪Wrapped in frost and snow♪

12:55.740 --> 12:56.659
Please believe me.

12:56.660 --> 12:58.239
♪Standing side by side with you♪

12:58.240 --> 12:59.339
Knowing what others think

12:59.340 --> 13:01.440
doesn't make me fulfilled.

13:02.820 --> 13:04.840
Right now, I only want to help you.

13:05.940 --> 13:07.560
I want to share some of your burden.

13:07.820 --> 13:09.659
I want to lighten the load
on your shoulders.

13:09.660 --> 13:13.910
♪Accumulated in this life,
now fulfilled♪

13:15.900 --> 13:17.360
Stay away from me.

13:17.920 --> 13:20.010
The further you are,
the lighter my burden will be.

13:21.100 --> 13:22.280
It's for your own good,

13:22.780 --> 13:23.819
and for mine.

13:23.820 --> 13:24.960
Why?

13:25.020 --> 13:26.400
I don't understand.

13:27.260 --> 13:28.600
Is it because of Wei Tingyu?

13:29.100 --> 13:30.579
Let's just say it is.

13:30.580 --> 13:32.020
What do you mean by “let's just say”?

13:32.580 --> 13:33.539
You're being childish.

13:33.540 --> 13:38.460
♪I devote my life and world
to your wishes♪

13:39.100 --> 13:40.240
Take care.

13:41.840 --> 13:44.309
♪Time bends and breaks♪

13:44.310 --> 13:48.870
♪For you, I rise again in this life♪

13:49.200 --> 13:54.100
♪Without regret♪

13:58.740 --> 13:59.960
We're getting extra training

14:00.100 --> 14:01.560
all thanks to the Duke of Jining.

14:01.940 --> 14:02.779
From now on,

14:02.780 --> 14:04.520
we're surely in for tough days.

14:04.540 --> 14:05.539
What are we going to do?

14:05.540 --> 14:06.539
- Duke!
- Stop talking.

14:06.540 --> 14:08.040
Duke...

14:08.100 --> 14:09.059
Duke...

14:09.060 --> 14:09.899
Duke, come here.

14:09.900 --> 14:10.779
Come, come.

14:10.780 --> 14:11.699
- Quickly.
- Please.

14:11.700 --> 14:12.579
Come, come.

14:12.580 --> 14:13.720
Quick, sit down.

14:14.580 --> 14:15.700
- Please sit.
- Wait...

14:15.710 --> 14:16.779
Song Mo hasn't arrived yet.

14:16.780 --> 14:17.910
I'm not supposed to sit down.

14:17.920 --> 14:19.659
This is how we usually do things.

14:19.660 --> 14:21.399
We sit down, report,
and discuss matters.

14:21.400 --> 14:22.779
In an hour, it's over.

14:22.780 --> 14:24.179
Yes. Please eat.

14:24.180 --> 14:25.320
Thank you.

14:29.740 --> 14:32.419
I heard Lord Song
is planning to discipline us.

14:32.420 --> 14:33.499
Discipline "us"?

14:33.500 --> 14:34.640
Just you.

14:34.660 --> 14:36.680
We're all just here to train with you.

14:36.940 --> 14:38.899
Exactly, it's all because of you.

14:38.900 --> 14:40.699
We're probably all in for tough times.

14:40.700 --> 14:41.840
That's right.

14:41.860 --> 14:43.000
What do you mean by that?

14:43.540 --> 14:44.739
Song Mo and Official Dou

14:44.740 --> 14:46.409
have a mountain of grudges.

14:46.410 --> 14:48.510
Lord Song and the Dou family
are like fire and water.

14:48.520 --> 14:49.890
Everyone knows that.

14:50.180 --> 14:52.140
You're the Dou family's
future son-in-law.

14:52.190 --> 14:54.420
Do you think he'll let you off?

14:56.900 --> 14:58.440
This is so unfair.

15:02.740 --> 15:03.960
Lord Song...

15:05.580 --> 15:07.240
Tribute candied olives.

15:07.500 --> 15:09.000
One piece costs 300 coins.

15:09.780 --> 15:10.960
Which one of you

15:11.980 --> 15:13.219
is so generous?

15:13.220 --> 15:14.299
The Duke.

15:14.300 --> 15:16.379
The Duke shared them with everyone
to boost morale.

15:16.380 --> 15:17.679
After all, our drills

15:17.680 --> 15:19.110
- never started this early.
- Hey...

15:19.120 --> 15:20.619
Yes, that's it.

15:20.620 --> 15:22.040
I see.

15:23.020 --> 15:25.379
In the military, there are rules
for standing and sitting.

15:25.380 --> 15:26.840
Private eating is strictly forbidden.

15:26.900 --> 15:28.240
Those who ate these

15:28.780 --> 15:30.259
will carry a one-stone weight

15:30.260 --> 15:31.720
and crawl for ten miles.

15:32.220 --> 15:33.899
Here, we speak only of military rank.

15:33.900 --> 15:35.659
We don't recognize titles or nobility.

15:35.660 --> 15:37.040
Anyone who disagrees

15:38.220 --> 15:39.360
will be dismissed from duty.

15:39.980 --> 15:41.120
As the instigator,

15:41.220 --> 15:42.600
you'll crawl an extra ten miles.

15:43.660 --> 15:45.000
But didn't you eat it too?

15:45.700 --> 15:46.920
Because I know

15:47.100 --> 15:50.080
the most important thing
in the military is unity.

15:52.500 --> 15:55.680
Today, I'll share the punishment
with you.

15:56.740 --> 15:57.659
Lord Song.

15:57.660 --> 15:59.179
Lord... no.

15:59.180 --> 16:00.320
Sir,

16:00.860 --> 16:01.650
it's their fault.

16:01.660 --> 16:02.890
I didn't even want to eat it.

16:02.900 --> 16:03.659
Silence! Move!

16:03.660 --> 16:05.459
Wait, sir, let me explain.

16:05.460 --> 16:06.720
- Hurry up!
- Keep up!

16:11.300 --> 16:12.440
Move, move!

16:12.820 --> 16:13.960
Hurry up!

16:20.700 --> 16:22.840
Keep moving, quickly!

16:24.060 --> 16:25.200
Faster!

16:38.660 --> 16:39.800
I can't do it anymore.

16:44.700 --> 16:45.840
Get up.

16:45.860 --> 16:47.000
I can't.

16:47.420 --> 16:48.640
I can't keep going.

16:50.100 --> 16:52.080
Lord Song, why are you making it
so hard for me?

16:52.140 --> 16:53.280
My lord!

16:57.060 --> 16:58.200
Well done.

17:02.900 --> 17:04.200
It's so high.

17:04.380 --> 17:06.040
How can I climb up there?

17:06.380 --> 17:07.899
Lord Song, please spare me.

17:07.900 --> 17:09.200
Anyone who doesn't make it

17:09.660 --> 17:10.920
won't get lunch.

17:12.140 --> 17:13.280
No food?

17:13.300 --> 17:14.299
That's not fair.

17:14.300 --> 17:15.659
Let's do this,

17:15.660 --> 17:17.600
you give me a hand and help me up, okay?

17:18.060 --> 17:19.200
Here.

17:20.900 --> 17:22.040
Take it.

17:22.380 --> 17:23.600
One, two.

17:35.900 --> 17:37.040
There's plenty for everyone.

17:37.420 --> 17:38.840
You're the Duke of Jining after all.

17:38.990 --> 17:40.750
Your eating manners are atrocious.

17:42.660 --> 17:44.120
Lord Song, you don't understand.

17:44.450 --> 17:45.800
I'm not used to physical training.

17:46.300 --> 17:47.699
This steamed bun today

17:47.700 --> 17:49.840
tastes better than all the delicacies
at my estate.

17:50.860 --> 17:53.240
Then I should seize the chance
to train you more.

17:54.180 --> 17:55.259
No, no.

17:55.260 --> 17:56.400
Please, Lord Song.

17:56.700 --> 17:58.539
Aren't we kindred spirits?

17:58.540 --> 17:59.469
Right?

17:59.470 --> 18:01.420
Why are you targeting me like this?

18:02.220 --> 18:04.599
I know, the Fourth Young Lady

18:04.600 --> 18:05.960
and I are engaged.

18:06.260 --> 18:09.030
But I have absolutely no intention
of siding with the Dou family.

18:11.420 --> 18:12.560
Duke,

18:13.060 --> 18:15.360
aren't you going to marry
the Fourth Young Lady?

18:18.260 --> 18:19.459
Marry her?

18:19.460 --> 18:20.920
It's all decided by our parents.

18:20.940 --> 18:22.240
I have no choice.

18:22.560 --> 18:25.059
You don't understand,
the Fourth Young Lady is rude and crude.

18:25.060 --> 18:26.560
We're not a good match at all.

18:34.980 --> 18:36.059
Lord Song.

18:36.060 --> 18:37.360
No, I mean

18:37.540 --> 18:38.680
sir,

18:39.140 --> 18:40.680
why are you looking at me like that?

18:43.300 --> 18:44.480
You're right.

18:45.220 --> 18:46.440
The Fourth Young Lady

18:46.980 --> 18:48.240
is indeed not a good person.

18:49.960 --> 18:51.440
You think so too?

18:54.020 --> 18:56.040
Great minds think alike.

18:56.500 --> 18:58.419
That Fourth Young Lady
was unfilial as a child,

18:58.420 --> 18:59.659
raised on a rural estate,

18:59.660 --> 19:01.189
and grew up among lowly people.

19:01.190 --> 19:03.310
She disregards her elders
and the rules of propriety.

19:03.320 --> 19:04.139
If not for her looks,

19:04.140 --> 19:05.979
she'd be utterly worthless.

19:05.980 --> 19:07.240
But, to be fair,

19:07.300 --> 19:08.920
she does have one good quality.

19:09.020 --> 19:11.200
She has good taste. She chose me.

19:11.740 --> 19:14.200
She's even urging her uncle
to set a date.

19:15.540 --> 19:16.659
Oh well,

19:16.660 --> 19:18.259
I'll just treat it as marrying

19:18.260 --> 19:20.699
a hen that lays golden eggs.

19:20.700 --> 19:22.120
Here, Lord Song,

19:22.700 --> 19:23.840
have an egg.

19:28.820 --> 19:29.490
You.

19:29.500 --> 19:31.210
Come train in riding and archery
with me.

19:31.220 --> 19:32.139
Lord Song...

19:32.140 --> 19:33.150
Lord Song...

19:33.160 --> 19:34.400
I haven't finished eating yet.

19:34.420 --> 19:36.730
- Aren't they kindred spirits?
- This kind of training is dangerous.

19:36.740 --> 19:39.240
It looks like the Duke won't survive.

19:39.420 --> 19:41.240
- Kindred spirit?
- Get on the horse.

19:41.300 --> 19:42.680
More like punching bag.

19:48.420 --> 19:50.040
(Tranquility and Serenity)

20:07.660 --> 20:11.699
(Yearning day and night, thousands
of words unsaid, longing to meet again.)

20:11.700 --> 20:13.110
I don't really understand paintings.

20:13.460 --> 20:16.080
But these verses are truly filled
with deep emotion.

20:17.660 --> 20:18.800
Sister,

20:18.820 --> 20:20.360
I swear I didn't seduce him.

20:20.740 --> 20:21.880
I swear.

20:21.940 --> 20:23.320
If you want me to believe you,

20:23.420 --> 20:24.920
then burn this painting.

20:42.260 --> 20:43.680
Since you like this painting,

20:44.540 --> 20:45.920
you should keep it.

20:47.420 --> 20:48.880
I don't like Wei Tingyu.

20:50.180 --> 20:51.680
Even though we're engaged,

20:51.740 --> 20:53.280
I will never marry him.

20:53.700 --> 20:55.640
So you were testing me earlier.

20:57.530 --> 20:59.240
But even so,

20:59.830 --> 21:01.820
Mother will never agree.

21:02.710 --> 21:04.240
She'll beat me to death.

21:04.790 --> 21:05.899
I know your mother

21:05.900 --> 21:07.219
has been harsh on you

21:07.220 --> 21:08.920
because of your failed
marriage prospects.

21:09.180 --> 21:11.120
But whether you learn painting
or calligraphy,

21:11.420 --> 21:12.680
or get married,

21:13.100 --> 21:15.440
it shouldn't be just to please her.

21:16.180 --> 21:17.600
You're an adult now.

21:17.940 --> 21:20.400
You should start making decisions
for your own life.

21:23.540 --> 21:26.040
(Yizhi Hall)

21:26.100 --> 21:27.579
Wei Tingyu is a foolish

21:27.580 --> 21:29.659
and dark-hearted man.

21:29.660 --> 21:31.400
He's unworthy of the Fourth Young Lady.

21:31.540 --> 21:32.880
He has countless flaws,

21:33.020 --> 21:35.000
yet he's engaged to Dou Zhao.

21:35.460 --> 21:37.299
He's engaged to her,

21:37.300 --> 21:39.240
yet he insults her behind her back.

21:39.260 --> 21:40.760
This man has terrible character.

21:40.860 --> 21:43.640
Should we tell the Fourth Young Lady
about this?

21:47.220 --> 21:48.720
But I still think

21:48.940 --> 21:50.299
Dou Zhao is lying.

21:50.300 --> 21:51.680
Stay away from me.

21:51.760 --> 21:53.800
The further you are,
the lighter my burden will be.

21:55.100 --> 21:56.320
It's for your own good

21:56.700 --> 21:58.000
and mine.

21:59.520 --> 22:01.160
I need to figure out
what she's thinking.

22:03.140 --> 22:04.280
Lord Song,

22:04.300 --> 22:05.800
a eunuch is outside asking for you.

22:06.580 --> 22:07.429
Let him in.

22:07.430 --> 22:08.600
Yes.

22:12.900 --> 22:14.040
Lord Song.

22:18.240 --> 22:20.459
The Duke of Jining says you injured him
during training

22:20.460 --> 22:21.800
out of personal grudge.

22:21.860 --> 22:23.659
He has rallied the sons of several dukes

22:23.660 --> 22:25.280
to submit a complaint to the palace.

22:25.300 --> 22:28.699
(Submitted by the Duke of Jining,
Wei Tingyu)

22:28.700 --> 22:30.000
This Wei Tingyu

22:30.620 --> 22:31.840
is quite interesting.

22:32.820 --> 22:33.699
(Guanghe Tower)

22:33.700 --> 22:40.440
♪A long clarity♪

22:41.220 --> 22:43.240
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

22:43.460 --> 22:49.320
♪A short clarity♪

22:49.500 --> 22:54.560
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

22:54.940 --> 22:57.960
In the end, it's still
about the engagement.

22:58.220 --> 23:00.610
Song Mo and Dou Shishu are on bad terms.

23:00.620 --> 23:02.430
Who would have thought
he'd extend his hatred

23:02.440 --> 23:04.080
and take revenge on Tingyu?

23:04.900 --> 23:06.259
You all saw it too,

23:06.260 --> 23:08.480
how much Tingyu has suffered.

23:11.180 --> 23:13.259
Why bother with a mad dog

23:13.260 --> 23:15.480
that bites indiscriminately?

23:15.540 --> 23:16.659
In my opinion,

23:16.660 --> 23:18.789
even though Song Mo has been reinstated,

23:18.790 --> 23:19.919
he spends all his time

23:19.920 --> 23:21.499
loitering around

23:21.500 --> 23:22.779
the opera house.

23:22.780 --> 23:24.099
What future does he have?

23:24.100 --> 23:25.320
Truly disgraceful.

23:25.460 --> 23:26.680
I've even heard

23:26.740 --> 23:28.040
that at night,

23:28.220 --> 23:31.080
he'd invite the performers
to give him foot massages.

23:31.120 --> 23:31.979
Really?

23:31.980 --> 23:34.480
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

23:35.020 --> 23:36.099
Pipe down,

23:36.100 --> 23:37.320
they're all regulars here.

23:39.700 --> 23:42.179
Ask Dou Shishu to find Tingyu a position

23:42.180 --> 23:43.739
(Duke of Jing)
at the Ministry of Rites.

23:43.740 --> 23:45.859
That should solve everything,
shouldn't it?

23:45.860 --> 23:47.120
For now,

23:47.340 --> 23:49.299
just focus on getting
this marriage done.

23:49.300 --> 23:51.120
Settle down first,
and then build a career.

23:52.220 --> 23:54.499
It wasn't easy to get
both families together

23:54.500 --> 23:55.960
to discuss the engagement.

23:56.260 --> 23:57.339
But look at you,

23:57.340 --> 23:59.400
you're fixated on the opera performance.

24:00.100 --> 24:02.619
The younger generation isn't interested.

24:02.620 --> 24:03.840
They've all left.

24:03.980 --> 24:06.120
Bravo!

24:07.940 --> 24:09.080
Fifth Young Lady.

24:09.180 --> 24:10.320
Fifth Young Lady.

24:10.380 --> 24:11.520
Fifth Young Lady.

24:11.620 --> 24:13.200
Why are you avoiding me?

24:13.260 --> 24:14.659
My parents are downstairs.

24:14.660 --> 24:15.800
Please leave.

24:15.860 --> 24:16.939
Fifth Young Lady,

24:16.940 --> 24:18.920
don't you know how I feel?

24:19.860 --> 24:21.400
It's impossible for us.

24:21.500 --> 24:23.360
These two truly seem
to have mutual feelings.

24:23.410 --> 24:25.810
Why doesn't the Duke propose
a new marriage?

24:25.820 --> 24:28.419
Him marrying the Fifth Young Lady
would be perfect for everyone.

24:28.420 --> 24:30.400
Perhaps Wei Tingzhen refused.

24:30.980 --> 24:32.400
This Wei Tingyu...

24:32.940 --> 24:35.320
If he had a spine,

24:35.580 --> 24:38.459
he wouldn't have given up
after just a few days on the job.

24:38.460 --> 24:39.799
Lately, I've heard that Lord Song

24:39.800 --> 24:43.010
was accused of misconduct
at the Imperial Guard training grounds.

24:43.060 --> 24:44.510
The Duke of Jining led the complaint,

24:44.520 --> 24:46.530
claiming he was severely injured
during training.

24:46.540 --> 24:48.059
Right after Lord Song learned

24:48.060 --> 24:49.579
about the Duke's engagement to you,

24:49.580 --> 24:51.739
he started targeting him.

24:51.740 --> 24:53.920
Why do you think he did that?

24:55.780 --> 24:57.040
Are you suggesting

24:57.060 --> 24:59.089
that Song Mo is jealous because of me?

24:59.090 --> 25:00.880
I didn't say that.

25:00.900 --> 25:02.059
But now that you mention it,

25:02.060 --> 25:03.440
it makes perfect sense.

25:03.780 --> 25:04.920
You...

25:07.940 --> 25:10.320
Wei Tingzhen, seeing that Song Mo
is out of reach,

25:10.330 --> 25:12.100
has started pushing
for the marriage again.

25:12.600 --> 25:15.379
I thought that winning first place
in the Ladies' Etiquette Contest

25:15.380 --> 25:17.920
would earn me an official position.

25:18.180 --> 25:20.520
That way, I could spend a few years
in Liaodong,

25:20.540 --> 25:22.160
and the marriage would be forgotten.

25:22.700 --> 25:24.280
- But now...
- No need to help me.

25:32.260 --> 25:33.259
Fourth Young Lady,

25:33.260 --> 25:35.160
you left the opera to come here.

25:35.420 --> 25:37.840
Are you secretly meeting your lover?

25:38.500 --> 25:39.880
I heard you

25:40.300 --> 25:42.560
take opera singers home every night
for foot massages.

25:42.780 --> 25:44.099
Cold feet at night

25:44.100 --> 25:46.160
is a sign of kidney deficiency.

25:48.100 --> 25:49.680
You should take care of your health.

25:53.380 --> 25:54.840
Let's leave.

25:58.820 --> 25:59.699
The Duke of Jining

25:59.700 --> 26:02.059
is bedridden from his training
at the Imperial Guard,

26:02.060 --> 26:03.960
yet you don't seem to worry about him.

26:04.500 --> 26:05.640
Instead,

26:06.340 --> 26:08.080
you seem more concerned about me.

26:13.980 --> 26:16.200
Do you really want to marry Wei Tingyu?

26:17.620 --> 26:19.619
Do you really need opera singers

26:19.620 --> 26:20.880
to sing you to sleep?

26:23.340 --> 26:26.600
I never could fool you.

26:32.060 --> 26:33.200
But you,

26:34.060 --> 26:35.920
you still haven't answered my question.

26:51.210 --> 26:52.099
Fourth Young Lady,

26:52.100 --> 26:53.240
why are you running away?

26:56.500 --> 26:57.640
What are you doing?

27:02.460 --> 27:04.040
Fourth Young Lady, are you all right?

27:05.130 --> 27:06.360
A dignified lord

27:06.460 --> 27:08.040
bullying a helpless woman?

27:20.260 --> 27:21.440
Helpless woman?

27:21.900 --> 27:25.320
That's not how you described her.

27:25.780 --> 27:26.920
I...

27:29.140 --> 27:30.339
What did I say about her?

27:30.340 --> 27:31.619
It doesn't matter.

27:31.620 --> 27:32.699
What matters

27:32.700 --> 27:34.400
is I saw you bullying her.

27:36.500 --> 27:37.640
Why are you laughing?

27:39.460 --> 27:40.339
Fourth Young Lady,

27:40.340 --> 27:41.480
don't be afraid.

27:42.020 --> 27:43.440
In broad daylight...

27:43.620 --> 27:44.760
no,

27:45.060 --> 27:46.400
under the bright moonlight,

27:47.380 --> 27:49.320
he wouldn't dare act improperly.

27:52.380 --> 27:53.419
What are you doing?

27:53.420 --> 27:54.560
You...

27:58.580 --> 27:59.720
Just you wait.

28:09.940 --> 28:11.160
Scoundrel.

28:13.660 --> 28:14.699
Fourth Young Lady.

28:14.700 --> 28:15.840
Mr. Wei.

28:16.380 --> 28:17.520
Please follow me.

28:22.340 --> 28:24.280
Bravo...

28:24.380 --> 28:25.520
Duke,

28:25.980 --> 28:27.520
we're alone now,

28:27.900 --> 28:29.760
so I'll speak frankly.

28:29.900 --> 28:31.040
- I...
- Say no more.

28:31.820 --> 28:33.160
I know you want to confess.

28:33.980 --> 28:36.539
You had your mother arrange
a marriage with my family,

28:36.540 --> 28:37.659
and even won

28:37.660 --> 28:39.200
the Ladies' Etiquette Contest for me.

28:40.460 --> 28:41.779
For you?

28:41.780 --> 28:42.699
Exactly.

28:42.700 --> 28:44.440
I know you're obsessed about me.

28:44.660 --> 28:46.219
I'm grateful for it.

28:46.220 --> 28:47.360
But the more you do this,

28:47.540 --> 28:49.379
the more uneasy I feel.

28:49.380 --> 28:50.640
Because I...

28:52.100 --> 28:53.240
Why did you kick me?

28:54.220 --> 28:55.259
I get it now.

28:55.260 --> 28:56.739
Emotionally speaking,

28:56.740 --> 28:57.699
I owe you

28:57.700 --> 28:58.590
an apology.

28:58.600 --> 29:00.299
It's only fair for you
to hit or scold me.

29:00.300 --> 29:01.440
But matters of the heart

29:01.540 --> 29:02.739
aren't up to anyone to decide.

29:02.740 --> 29:04.739
Even if you win my body,
you won't win my heart.

29:04.740 --> 29:05.920
Enough, Duke.

29:10.300 --> 29:12.360
I know your heart isn't with me.

29:12.420 --> 29:14.080
You love someone else.

29:14.260 --> 29:16.760
So why not annul our engagement
and marry her instead?

29:16.940 --> 29:17.939
Marriage is a matter

29:17.940 --> 29:19.960
decided by parents and matchmakers.

29:20.660 --> 29:23.360
I've lost both my parents,
and my sister is like a mother to me.

29:23.700 --> 29:25.000
I dare not go against her wishes.

29:26.060 --> 29:28.280
I know this is unfair to you

29:29.100 --> 29:30.880
and even more unfair
to the one I truly love.

29:31.660 --> 29:34.240
If Dou Shishu could intervene,

29:36.820 --> 29:38.320
things would be so much easier.

29:39.140 --> 29:41.470
(You and Dou Ming are the ones
who are mutually in love.)

29:41.480 --> 29:44.040
(You won't fight for your love,
and you expect me to?)

29:44.580 --> 29:45.659
(If I were Dou Ming,)

29:45.660 --> 29:46.900
(I'd have slapped you already.)

29:47.940 --> 29:49.080
Fine.

29:50.420 --> 29:52.120
Since you can't decide,

29:52.740 --> 29:54.979
let both families follow tradition

29:54.980 --> 29:56.300
and perform a marriage divination.

29:57.820 --> 29:58.960
Marriage divination?

29:59.620 --> 30:02.280
There's no need to rush things.

30:02.820 --> 30:05.459
Let me go home and discuss this

30:05.460 --> 30:07.680
with my sister.

30:07.700 --> 30:09.000
I'll take my leave now.

30:11.820 --> 30:13.440
A marriage divination?

30:13.660 --> 30:15.499
Wei Tingyu hesitates and doesn't act.

30:15.500 --> 30:16.680
He's truly spineless.

30:17.020 --> 30:18.779
No wonder Lord Song
despises him so much.

30:18.780 --> 30:20.259
Even I want to punch him.

30:20.260 --> 30:22.120
He's passive, noncommittal,
and irresponsible,

30:22.300 --> 30:23.979
leaving all the tough decisions
to women.

30:23.980 --> 30:26.340
He truly has the temperament
of someone raised among women.

30:26.350 --> 30:27.600
Completely unreliable.

30:28.700 --> 30:30.340
I wonder what Dou Ming thinks of this.

30:30.350 --> 30:31.440
As for the Fifth Young Lady,

30:31.450 --> 30:33.340
I've quietly sent someone
to keep an eye on her.

30:33.350 --> 30:36.680
But do you really want
to leave this to fate

30:36.700 --> 30:38.080
and rely on divination?

30:38.820 --> 30:40.000
Fate?

30:42.780 --> 30:44.440
Fate sounds perfect.

30:44.660 --> 30:47.600
No one can defy fate.

30:52.100 --> 30:54.080
Just as you expected, Lord Song.

30:54.260 --> 30:57.379
Deep down, the Fourth Young Lady doesn't want
to marry Wei Tingyu either.

30:57.380 --> 30:59.680
She's just putting on a facade.

31:00.220 --> 31:02.480
Then let her finish her act.

31:03.180 --> 31:05.200
(Memorial)

31:08.300 --> 31:10.640
These are memorials submitted recently

31:11.260 --> 31:13.080
by the Duke of Jining
and the Duke of Jing.

31:13.700 --> 31:15.160
Tell Wei Tingyu

31:15.580 --> 31:16.760
that if he wants to complain,

31:16.920 --> 31:18.979
he should first master archery
and horseback riding

31:18.980 --> 31:21.240
and become a proper duke
before coming forward.

31:21.620 --> 31:23.120
From now on,

31:23.630 --> 31:25.000
do not present his memorials to me.

31:25.940 --> 31:27.080
Understood.

31:27.430 --> 31:30.499
Your Majesty, although Song Mo holds an important
post in the Imperial Guard,

31:30.500 --> 31:32.299
he spends his nights at the opera house,

31:32.300 --> 31:34.480
disturbing respectable women.

31:34.620 --> 31:37.560
It tarnishes the court's reputation.

31:37.980 --> 31:40.099
However, Song Mo has indeed fixed

31:40.100 --> 31:41.899
the lax atmosphere
in the Imperial Guard.

31:41.900 --> 31:44.520
Your family and the Duke of Jining's
family have an engagement.

31:44.820 --> 31:45.960
Official Dou,

31:46.240 --> 31:48.440
surely your remarks aren't driven
by personal motives?

31:48.460 --> 31:49.600
You...

31:52.340 --> 31:53.920
No one is perfect.

31:54.380 --> 31:56.200
Since he has let go of the past

31:56.260 --> 31:58.080
and is wholeheartedly loyal
to the court,

31:58.620 --> 31:59.760
I am pleased.

32:01.020 --> 32:02.320
You two,

32:02.660 --> 32:05.360
in private, are in-laws,

32:05.380 --> 32:08.440
but in public, you are pillars
of the court.

32:08.620 --> 32:12.360
Must you attack each other
in front of me over private matters?

32:13.860 --> 32:15.920
- We are at fault.
- We are at fault.

32:22.460 --> 32:26.160
Cultivate the family, govern the state,
bring peace to the world.

32:27.100 --> 32:28.379
Without family,

32:28.380 --> 32:30.680
a person is like a kite
with a broken string.

32:30.820 --> 32:32.240
Ungrounded.

32:32.340 --> 32:33.739
Whether it's Yantang

32:33.740 --> 32:36.320
or the Dou and the Wei families,

32:37.300 --> 32:39.800
don't repeat the Wu family's mistake

32:40.480 --> 32:43.540
and turn the court
into a laughing stock.

32:44.180 --> 32:45.400
We understand.

32:45.500 --> 32:46.640
Yes, Your Majesty.

32:47.020 --> 32:51.480
(Aspire for Greatness)

32:52.100 --> 32:53.240
Ill?

32:53.860 --> 32:54.979
She has just agreed

32:54.980 --> 32:56.859
to perform the marriage divination.

32:56.860 --> 32:58.219
How could she fall ill so suddenly?

32:58.220 --> 33:00.640
The Fourth Young Lady said
it's because of the cold weather.

33:00.760 --> 33:02.080
Her spirits are fine,

33:02.140 --> 33:03.749
but her forehead is still burning hot.

33:03.750 --> 33:04.890
She can't get out of bed.

33:05.040 --> 33:06.099
Have you called a doctor?

33:06.100 --> 33:08.819
Make sure to take good care of her,
lest her illness worsens.

33:08.820 --> 33:09.960
Yes.

33:12.930 --> 33:14.480
She agreed to the marriage divination.

33:14.660 --> 33:16.019
At least she's come around.

33:16.020 --> 33:17.980
She's not as resistant
to the marriage anymore.

33:18.100 --> 33:20.600
Why do you still look so troubled?

33:21.750 --> 33:22.890
Nothing.

33:23.180 --> 33:24.560
I was just thinking,

33:24.580 --> 33:26.560
since this is a marriage divination,

33:26.780 --> 33:28.339
isn't it inauspicious

33:28.340 --> 33:29.960
to fall ill now?

33:30.380 --> 33:31.960
The birth dates have been matched.

33:31.980 --> 33:34.680
Burning tortoise shells
is just a formality.

33:38.140 --> 33:39.640
Seventh Master, Seventh Madam.

33:40.660 --> 33:42.440
The Duchess of Jing has arrived.

33:46.180 --> 33:48.880
This is the renowned Mr. Ma
from the Capital.

33:49.060 --> 33:51.760
He's performed readings
for many noble families.

33:55.380 --> 33:56.960
Okay, you may leave.

34:02.340 --> 34:03.480
Ming.

34:04.260 --> 34:05.400
Ming.

34:06.580 --> 34:07.720
Ming.

34:12.180 --> 34:13.320
Ming.

34:14.380 --> 34:16.000
What are you doing?

34:16.260 --> 34:17.299
I wrote you letters,

34:17.300 --> 34:18.270
but you didn't reply.

34:18.280 --> 34:19.539
So I came to see you in person.

34:19.540 --> 34:20.870
Go back. I don't want to see you.

34:20.880 --> 34:21.920
Don't push me.

34:22.740 --> 34:23.880
Are you hurt?

34:25.570 --> 34:26.419
Are you all right?

34:26.420 --> 34:27.560
I'm fine.

34:28.100 --> 34:29.720
You just got into trouble recently.

34:29.740 --> 34:30.779
If someone

34:30.780 --> 34:32.040
sees us like this,

34:32.540 --> 34:33.800
you'll be condemned.

34:34.940 --> 34:36.440
So you're worried about me?

34:41.860 --> 34:43.779
- Well?
- No sign of Wei Tingyu.

34:43.780 --> 34:46.720
They say he and the Duke of Jing
don't believe in these superstitions.

34:47.220 --> 34:49.360
It seems they're pressed
and looking for a solution.

34:50.020 --> 34:51.379
What about the marriage divination?

34:51.380 --> 34:53.139
Wei Tingzhen said,
as the eldest sister,

34:53.140 --> 34:54.280
she will head the ritual.

34:56.300 --> 34:57.819
Tell Mr. Chen and Su Lan

34:57.820 --> 34:58.960
to act.

35:18.460 --> 35:19.770
Ming, don't worry.

35:19.780 --> 35:21.299
Everyone is in the main hall right now,

35:21.300 --> 35:22.610
performing the divination ritual.

35:22.640 --> 35:23.680
No one will come here.

35:23.880 --> 35:25.259
I just have a few heartfelt words.

35:25.260 --> 35:26.540
Once I've said them, I'll leave.

35:28.080 --> 35:29.600
They're already performing divination.

35:29.660 --> 35:30.899
What else is there to say?

35:30.900 --> 35:32.300
Even if you say it, I won't listen.

35:33.180 --> 35:34.939
- Leave now.
- Ming.

35:34.940 --> 35:36.560
This is all my sister's doing.

35:36.660 --> 35:37.800
I...

35:44.540 --> 35:45.539
Give it back.

35:45.540 --> 35:46.720
Give it back.

35:46.820 --> 35:48.400
Red beans grow in the southern country.

35:48.580 --> 35:50.200
In spring, how many will sprout?

35:58.060 --> 35:59.200
Look.

36:10.660 --> 36:12.360
Our hearts are clearly connected.

36:12.940 --> 36:14.080
Why do you...

36:15.940 --> 36:17.680
I've sent someone to inquire.

36:17.780 --> 36:20.880
Besides reading poetry and painting,

36:21.540 --> 36:22.680
your favorite pastime

36:22.820 --> 36:25.240
is visiting the Drunken Bordello.

36:25.260 --> 36:26.299
Your house is filled

36:26.300 --> 36:27.939
with countless beautiful maids.

36:27.940 --> 36:29.059
Even when painting,

36:29.060 --> 36:31.240
you need several maids
to prepare your ink and brushes.

36:31.660 --> 36:33.160
Why do you still come to see me?

36:41.660 --> 36:42.939
Heaven and earth as witnesses,

36:42.940 --> 36:44.539
I, Wei Tingyu, hereby swear,

36:44.540 --> 36:45.579
that from today onward,

36:45.580 --> 36:47.360
I will dismiss all the maids
in my residence

36:47.370 --> 36:49.040
and never step foot in a brothel again.

36:49.220 --> 36:50.360
From now on,

36:51.940 --> 36:53.760
I will only paint Dou Ming.

36:54.420 --> 36:55.640
If I break this vow,

36:55.660 --> 36:58.060
may I be pierced by swords
with no place to rest in death.

36:59.900 --> 37:01.440
I haven't even said yes.

37:02.140 --> 37:03.920
Why make such a harsh vow?

37:08.700 --> 37:10.040
Do you believe me now?

37:13.380 --> 37:15.240
Even if you really love me,

37:15.760 --> 37:18.000
you still wouldn't defy your sister.

37:18.780 --> 37:20.600
And I don't want to disgrace my family.

37:22.420 --> 37:23.560
Don't worry.

37:23.700 --> 37:25.080
I've already thought of a solution.

37:25.660 --> 37:26.800
Let me show you something.

37:28.420 --> 37:30.659
Someone! Thief!

37:30.660 --> 37:31.899
- Thief!
- Quick, run.

37:31.900 --> 37:33.339
- Thief!
- Go.

37:33.340 --> 37:34.199
- Someone!
- Ming.

37:34.200 --> 37:35.760
I haven't shown you this yet.

37:38.710 --> 37:40.419
- Catch the thief!
- Search the courtyard.

37:40.420 --> 37:41.680
Catch the thief!

37:41.690 --> 37:42.790
- Quick!
- Catch the thief!

37:42.800 --> 37:44.080
Don't let him escape.

37:44.120 --> 37:45.900
How could there be a thief
in broad daylight?

37:45.910 --> 37:46.779
Seventh Master,

37:46.780 --> 37:48.699
it seems he's run
into the inner courtyard.

37:48.700 --> 37:49.939
They're going after him now.

37:49.940 --> 37:50.779
Hurry.

37:50.780 --> 37:52.400
Are Dou Ming and Dou Zhao still there?

37:52.940 --> 37:54.920
Yes, go check on Ming.

37:55.660 --> 37:57.659
Madam Wei, please stay here for now.

37:57.660 --> 37:59.520
What's the capital turning into?

37:59.580 --> 38:01.120
There are thieves everywhere.

38:01.420 --> 38:02.560
This is ridiculous.

38:03.520 --> 38:05.230
- Hurry.
- Take a look at this pouch first.

38:05.240 --> 38:06.900
This is no time for that. Hurry and leave.

38:06.910 --> 38:08.259
You haven't seen what's in it yet.

38:08.260 --> 38:10.099
- Now is not the time.
- Someone, catch the thief!

38:10.100 --> 38:11.139
Quick, run.

38:11.140 --> 38:11.979
Check over there.

38:11.980 --> 38:12.819
- Ming.
- Quickly.

38:12.820 --> 38:14.360
Don't forget to check the pouch.

38:16.940 --> 38:18.920
Young Lady.

38:19.440 --> 38:20.579
Young Lady, are you alright?

38:20.580 --> 38:21.720
I'm fine.

38:37.540 --> 38:39.760
(Wei Tingyu, Dou Zhao)

38:42.380 --> 38:43.920
(It's exactly the same.)

38:44.060 --> 38:45.400
("Good fortune" again.)

38:45.820 --> 38:47.240
(At this rate,)

38:47.420 --> 38:49.360
(I fear it'll lead to heartbreak again.)

39:04.220 --> 39:05.360
Quickly, go.

39:07.420 --> 39:08.720
"Bad fortune."

39:09.700 --> 39:11.600
Raising false alarms about a thief.

39:11.620 --> 39:13.450
(Wei Tingyu, Dou Zhao)
She thinks she can annul the engagement

39:13.460 --> 39:15.200
with such a cheap trick?

39:15.340 --> 39:16.720
Disrespecting gods and spirits.

39:16.940 --> 39:18.539
No wonder she's a motherless child.

39:18.540 --> 39:20.339
Luckily, Madam anticipated this

39:20.340 --> 39:21.899
and had some tortoise shells

39:21.900 --> 39:23.840
marked with “good fortune"
prepared in advance.

39:24.300 --> 39:26.379
The wisdom of age prevails.

39:26.380 --> 39:27.939
When she agreed to the divination,

39:27.940 --> 39:30.120
I knew she would cheat.

39:31.940 --> 39:33.080
Someone's coming.

39:33.740 --> 39:34.779
They're back?

39:34.780 --> 39:36.080
- Quick.
- Quick.

39:45.620 --> 39:46.880
Ming.

39:47.000 --> 39:48.140
Shh.

39:54.700 --> 39:57.280
(Wei Tingyu, Dou Zhao)

40:08.300 --> 40:09.440
This...

40:10.500 --> 40:11.419
How could it be?

40:11.420 --> 40:13.360
Bad fortune?

40:14.100 --> 40:16.400
When did Ming come up with this idea?

40:17.340 --> 40:18.459
Quick, swap it.

40:18.460 --> 40:19.600
Don't let Ming...

40:20.620 --> 40:22.779
Ming took away the tongs.

40:22.780 --> 40:24.400
Then use your hands.

40:25.940 --> 40:27.219
Madam, it's scalding.

40:27.220 --> 40:28.939
- Useless fool! I'll do it.
- It's hot.

40:28.940 --> 40:29.939
Be careful, Madam.

40:29.940 --> 40:31.219
Be careful...

40:31.220 --> 40:32.480
Quickly.

40:32.780 --> 40:34.160
(Wei Tingyu, Dou Zhao)
There.

40:35.140 --> 40:36.179
Someone's coming. Quick.

40:36.180 --> 40:37.320
Quick.

40:37.580 --> 40:38.720
We checked.

40:39.140 --> 40:40.779
Some house guests

40:40.780 --> 40:41.960
must have made a mistake

40:42.060 --> 40:43.480
and thought they saw a thief.

40:43.930 --> 40:45.400
Sorry for the disturbance, Madam Wei.

40:46.460 --> 40:47.920
No harm done.

40:48.940 --> 40:50.219
Male water, female metal.

40:50.220 --> 40:52.699
(Wei Tingyu, Dou Zhao)
There are no cracks in the match.

40:52.700 --> 40:54.760
This is very good fortune.

40:55.060 --> 40:56.179
First, it entails wealth.

40:56.180 --> 40:57.699
Second, success in career.

40:57.700 --> 40:58.719
What about children,

40:58.720 --> 41:00.600
the most important thing?

41:00.740 --> 41:03.000
Of course, in great abundance!

41:03.140 --> 41:04.659
If this couple weds,

41:04.660 --> 41:06.520
it will bring blessings
to both families.

41:07.140 --> 41:08.259
Wonderful.

41:08.260 --> 41:09.099
In my opinion,

41:09.100 --> 41:11.419
this wedding should be settled quickly.

41:11.420 --> 41:13.640
There's an auspicious date next month.

41:13.860 --> 41:15.459
As the mistress of my family,

41:15.460 --> 41:17.480
I've already prepared the bridal dowry.

41:25.930 --> 41:28.179
After all this, it still turned
out to be "good fortune".

41:28.180 --> 41:29.400
How frustrating.

41:31.380 --> 41:33.360
Someone's here. I'll explain later.

41:33.580 --> 41:34.539
Do as I instructed.

41:34.540 --> 41:35.680
Yes.

41:39.900 --> 41:41.360
Madam Wei, please wait.

41:42.580 --> 41:43.720
Madam Wei.

41:43.980 --> 41:45.200
Weren't you unwell?

41:45.820 --> 41:49.200
I'm sorry I was disrespectful
and offended you.

41:49.540 --> 41:50.739
These lily bulbs

41:50.740 --> 41:52.979
were imported from Jiangnan.

41:52.980 --> 41:54.120
Please accept them

41:54.700 --> 41:56.000
as a token of apology

41:56.260 --> 41:58.379
and our harmonious relationship.

41:58.380 --> 42:00.960
I hope this marriage
can be settled quickly.

42:01.620 --> 42:03.240
This illness

42:03.300 --> 42:05.000
has really changed you.

42:06.620 --> 42:07.760
Thank you.

42:15.940 --> 42:18.120
Wang Yingxue is clever,

42:19.140 --> 42:21.299
so I must always think
one step ahead of her.

42:21.300 --> 42:23.440
It doesn't matter
what the tortoise shells say.

42:23.900 --> 42:25.040
What matters is

42:25.180 --> 42:26.920
we arouse Wei Tingzhen's suspicion.

42:27.100 --> 42:28.899
Wei Tingzhen already harbored doubts.

42:28.900 --> 42:30.699
With you suddenly being so nice to her,

42:30.700 --> 42:32.179
she's bound to investigate thoroughly.

42:32.180 --> 42:34.229
So,

42:34.230 --> 42:35.670
what will she investigate?

42:36.340 --> 42:37.899
I need you two

42:37.900 --> 42:39.400
to put on a show.

42:54.620 --> 42:55.739
Once she's married,

42:55.740 --> 42:57.019
Dou Zhao

42:57.020 --> 42:58.109
and her family assets

42:58.110 --> 43:00.779
will be under your control.

43:00.780 --> 43:02.639
I only wish

43:02.640 --> 43:04.419
that the person I love

43:04.420 --> 43:05.939
can have a fulfilling life.

43:05.940 --> 43:07.010
(Duke of Jining's Residence)

43:07.020 --> 43:07.920
Wait.

43:09.950 --> 43:12.620
♪The golden fiery steed rides
across the vast horizon♪

43:13.230 --> 43:16.330
♪In this life, oh♪

43:16.480 --> 43:18.159
♪Without you♪

43:18.160 --> 43:21.780
♪What is there to envy?♪

43:22.240 --> 43:24.719
♪Let me lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles♪

43:24.720 --> 43:29.039
♪To adorn your hair with a jade hairpin♪

43:29.040 --> 43:31.229
♪Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms♪

43:31.230 --> 43:35.680
♪Bloom in a single night for you♪

43:35.830 --> 43:38.959
♪The splendor of the world
is but fleeting sorrow♪

43:38.960 --> 43:42.050
♪Should the flames of war arise♪

43:42.390 --> 43:45.639
♪I shall hold your hand♪

43:45.640 --> 43:48.619
♪And walk through the dust♪

43:48.620 --> 43:50.829
♪I want to hold you in my arms♪

43:50.830 --> 43:55.119
♪Leaving the world behind♪

43:55.120 --> 43:57.429
♪From now on, all the vast wonders
of the world♪

43:57.430 --> 44:01.679
♪May be left as blank spaces♪

44:01.680 --> 44:05.380
♪The dazzling spring moon over the city♪

44:05.560 --> 44:08.620
♪Is no match for your beauty♪

44:08.790 --> 44:14.000
♪Why ascend to high towers again?♪

44:14.800 --> 44:17.059
♪I will lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles♪

44:17.060 --> 44:18.699
♪Break my spear to crown you♪

44:18.700 --> 44:21.419
♪With a golden-branch hairpin♪

44:21.420 --> 44:23.539
♪Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms♪

44:23.540 --> 44:27.649
♪Bloom for you♪

44:27.650 --> 44:31.410
♪No more guarding lonely towers♪

44:31.450 --> 44:34.769
♪Spring is near, ripe for the taking♪

44:34.770 --> 44:36.109
♪Holding your hand♪

44:36.110 --> 44:41.060
♪Till we reach beyond the noise♪

44:41.500 --> 44:44.650
♪Only for you, I shall paint♪

44:44.840 --> 44:47.630
♪With bold strokes and vibrant colors♪

44:47.820 --> 44:49.669
♪And for all else♪

44:49.670 --> 44:56.660
♪Let it remain pale and void♪

44:59.140 --> 45:00.179
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:00.180 --> 45:01.099
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:01.100 --> 45:02.360
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
